FIPS - Class in com.nxp.id.jcopx
FIPS is a JCOP proprietary extension for executing and checking FIPS self-tests by an applet, after power-up.
FIPS() - Constructor for class com.nxp.id.jcopx.FIPS
 
FIPS_SELFTESTS_AES_DEC_MASK - Static variable in class com.nxp.id.jcopx.FIPS
Enable FIPS_SELFTESTS_AES_DEC_MASK to execute AES decryption self-test or to check self-test result.
